Package: shinyOTP
Type: Package
Title: Shiny Module for OTP (One-Time Password) Authentication
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Giuseppe Dejan", 
           family = "Lucido", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "dejanlucdo@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Giuseppe Dejan Lucido <dejanlucdo@gmail.com>
Description: Provides UI and server modules for implementing One-Time Password (OTP) 
    authentication in Shiny applications. It allows sending OTP via email and verifying
    the OTP within the app, making it easy to integrate basic authentication into Shiny apps.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
